highlights.text: “Believer” by Imagine Dragons has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 334 weeks straight.
“fukumean” by Gunna is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 97 spots at #48.
Peso Pluma has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “Ella Baila Sola” is the highest at #1.
“LADY GAGA” by Peso Pluma, Gabito Ballesteros, and Junior H is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #9.
